  "descriptionShort": "Number of people who do not have an improved water source at home, but use an [improved drinking water source](#dod:improved-water-source) where collection takes no more than 30 minutes for a roundtrip.",
  "descriptionFromProducer": "Use of improved drinking water sources no more than 30 mins roundtrip, but not safely managed",
